@startuml
title C2 - Diagrama de Contenedores - AngeloDjangoOrders

' ============================================================
' C2 - Diagrama de contenedores
' Muestra las partes grandes del sistema:
' navegador, aplicación Django, base de datos y Docker Compose.
' ============================================================

left to right direction

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 14
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #DBEAFE
  BorderColor #2563EB
  FontColor #0F172A
}

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}

skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #DCFCE7
  BorderColor #15803D
  FontColor #0F172A
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FEF3C7
  BorderColor #F59E0B
  FontColor #0F172A
}

actor "Usuario\nCliente / Admin" as User

rectangle "Navegador Web\nHTML + CSS + JS\nBootstrap local" as Browser

package "Docker Compose\nangelow" {

  rectangle "Contenedor web\nPython + Django" as Web {
    rectangle "Proyecto dcrm" as Dcrm
    rectangle "App website" as Website
    rectangle "Templates / Static" as Static
  }

  database "Contenedor db\nMySQL 8.4\nBase: clientes" as DB
}

rectangle "Variables de entorno\nDJANGO_DB_HOST=db\nDJANGO_DB_NAME=clientes" as Env

rectangle "docker/entrypoint.sh\nmigrate + runserver" as Entrypoint

User --> Browser : usa la interfaz
Browser --> Web : HTTP\nlocalhost:8000

Web --> DB : ORM Django\nMySQL db:3306

Env --> Web : configuración\nbase de datos
Entrypoint --> Web : inicia aplicación

note bottom of Web
El contenedor web ejecuta Django,
carga plantillas, archivos estáticos
y procesa las vistas del sistema.
end note

note bottom of DB
La base de datos conserva usuarios,
clientes, pedidos, ítems e historial.
end note

legend bottom
C2 muestra los contenedores principales del sistema.
No detalla clases, vistas ni formularios internos.
endlegend

@enduml